Sentencas: CH4-fueled metal-supported solid oxide fuel cells (CH4-MS-SOFCs) are propitious as CH4 is low-priced and readily available, and its renewable production is possible, such as biomethane.
Titulo: Nanocomposite Catalyst for High-Performance and Durable Intermediate-Temperature Methane-Fueled Metal-Supported Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: However, the current CH4-MS-SOFCs suffer from either poor power density or short durable operation, which is ascribed to the low catalytic activity and poor coking tolerance of the metallic anode support.
Titulo: Nanocomposite Catalyst for High-Performance and Durable Intermediate-Temperature Methane-Fueled Metal-Supported Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: Herein, we have deliberately designed and synthesized a highly active nanocomposite catalyst, Sm-doped CeO2- supported Ni, as the internal steam methane reforming catalyst, to optimize CH4-MS-SOFCs.
Titulo: Nanocomposite Catalyst for High-Performance and Durable Intermediate-Temperature Methane-Fueled Metal-Supported Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: Both power densities and durability of optimized CH4-MS-SOFCs have been dramatically enhanced compared to the pristine CH4-MS-SOFCs.
Titulo: Nanocomposite Catalyst for High-Performance and Durable Intermediate-Temperature Methane-Fueled Metal-Supported Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: The optimized CH4-MS-SOFCs deliver the highest performances among all zirconia-based CH4-MS-SOFCs.
Titulo: Nanocomposite Catalyst for High-Performance and Durable Intermediate-Temperature Methane-Fueled Metal-Supported Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: Furthermore, the operating temperature has been reduced to 600 degrees C.
Titulo: Nanocomposite Catalyst for High-Performance and Durable Intermediate-Temperature Methane-Fueled Metal-Supported Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: At 600 degrees C, a viable peak power density of >350 mW/cm2 is achieved, which is more than three times as high as the pristine CH4-MS-SOFCs.
Titulo: Nanocomposite Catalyst for High-Performance and Durable Intermediate-Temperature Methane-Fueled Metal-Supported Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: Furthermore, the optimized CH4-MS-SOFC achieves >1000 h of stable operation.
Titulo: Nanocomposite Catalyst for High-Performance and Durable Intermediate-Temperature Methane-Fueled Metal-Supported Solid Oxide Fuel Cells
